description: Describes the available OpsWorks Stacks agent versions. You must specify a stack ID or a configuration manager. DescribeAgentVersions returns a list of available agent versions for the specified stack or configuration manager.

parameters.name: ConfigurationManager
parameters.description: The configuration manager. Name (string) --- The name. This parameter must be set to Chef. Version (string) --- The Chef version. This parameter must be set to 12, 11.10, or 11.4 for Linux stacks, and to 12.2 for Windows stacks. The default value for Linux stacks is 12.

nested_items.name: AgentVersions
nested_items.description: The agent versions for the specified stack or configuration manager. Note that this value is the complete version number, not the abbreviated number used by the console.
